== Ubuzima bwo hambere ==
Yavukiye kandi akurira i [[Kigali]], umurwa mukuru w'u [[Rwanda]], ubwana bwa Nadege bwarimo uburambe bwo kwigunga no kwiheba, ibyo bikaba byaramuteye imbaraga zo gutangira kwandika ibisigo kugira ngo agaragaze ibitekerezo bye n'urugendo rwo gukira.  Amashuri yisumbuye yarangije muri Saint Andre, kuri ubu akaba akurikirana impamyabumenyi ihanitse ya Business Communication muri kaminuza ya New New Hampshire binyuze muri kaminuza ya Kepler ikorera i Kigali. <ref name="Nzabonimpa" /> <ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/202106290340.html</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mu rwego rwo guhangana n’ihungabana no kwiheba biturutse ku ivangura yahuye na ryo mu mashuri yisumbuye, mu 2020 Nadege yarangije asohora igitabo cye cya mbere yise ''First Creation'',, icyegeranyo cy’imivugo. <ref>https://igihe.com/umuco/ibitabo/article/uko-ubwanditsi-bwafashije-uwayezu-nadege-gukira-agahinda-k-uburyo-sosiyete</ref> Nadege yasohoye igitabo cye cya kabiri mu Gushyingo 2021, ''Light In The Dark'', urwibutso rugufi rw'inkuru ye kuva ku myaka 9 kugeza ku myaka 16. <ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/article/sandra-nadege-yanditse-igitabo-ku-buzima-bugoye-yanyuzemo</ref> <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/dropped-pins-how-make-google-maps-more-efficient</ref>

